  button(style="font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 16px 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #003b6b; border: none; background-color: #f2d60f; text-align: center;") #[a(style="text-decoration: none; color: #003b6b;" target="_blank" href="https://www.arctics.academy/") 試用平台]
  p Arctics團隊 敬上